!begin_node Cookie, LTMF

(!B)LETEMFLY.PRG or LET_LGHT.PRG(!b) - Let 'em Fly!

Replaces/extends almost all form_xxxx routines of the (!nolink [AES]). Thanks to 
this many dialogs are now: a) flight-capable, b) operable via the 
keyboard and c) provided with additional functions for editable 
fields. Furthermore, the cookie jar will now offer a flying routine 
for non-form_do dialogs.

Modifies: TRAP #2 ((!nolink [AES/VDI])), TRAP #13 ((!nolink [BIOS])).

Status: Freeware.

!end_node

